# Web app uses no env vars. All config lives in:
#   ~/.config/neko/config.json   — DB connection (auto-populated by /setup)
#   ~/.config/neko/secret-key    — at-rest encryption key (auto-generated)
# plus the metadata DB itself for everything else (LLM provider, agent
# backend, data source, research).
#
# The DEMO toggle is the one allowed knob — uncomment to flip into the
# canned-mock briefing flow for screenshots / video without real data.
#
# DEMO=true
